{"tid":1257373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要打倒保皇黨 成立賣港database有得諗！","createTime":"2019-06-25T13:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T17:26:11.000Z","uid":221265,"like":113,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"efb0af44291281aa186a97e9ccef1664a8529c43","tid":1257373,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"11月區選<br />\n<br />\n保皇黨最驚係乜  麥美娟都要屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n就係喺616前成班保皇喺立會 行會支持林鄭推送中條例<br />\n<br />\n要highlight依個point, 唔好俾啲梁美芬 李慧瓊扮成功爭取林鄭暫緩<br />\n<br />\n之後好多agenda，包括送黃金靚地俾解放軍<br />\n<br />\n包括明日大嶼 國歌法，依家佢哋想拖得就拖 怕11月前支持林鄭失選票<br />\n<br />\n要迫佢哋表態 <br />\n<br />\n區會依家完全由保皇黨控制 ，個撚個都賣港<br />\n<br />\n如果有個賣港database,分晒18區去數到佢哋點賣港，有幾多利益衝突，<br />\n<br />\n有無得諗？<br />\n<br />\n區選多啲自己人，唔洗再搞啲垃圾嘉年華，唔駛俾保皇用咁多區會資源 <br />\n為自己養票。"},{"pid":"dde245070e627b8e97f8ac629ba64f52f100a4be","tid":1257373,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"290c8ead957b0e0ef12444ced56b127d3406a4ad","tid":1257373,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"558a7778de5f4cb332fb47dd2711084ffac70cf9","tid":1257373,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96479bdd85255876b71c27e4f54753a11ae33db5","tid":1257373,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a3a5ad9cf38023b3a42284cd7adbd24b0528847c","tid":1257373,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"果啲咩家教會<br />\n我哋搵自己人滲透返"},{"pid":"16fab8b78b83548a8e9d133dabe369fe70e75568","tid":1257373,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:06:00.000Z","msg":"城寨友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e339644958eb40c35775aa9acb094bb39262c396","tid":1257373,"uid":221265,"like"